    <title>VT 技术学习 (一) 检测支持与VMXON</title>
    <url>/2021/12/09/VT-%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0-%E4%B8%80-%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8EVMXON/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><ul>
<li><strong>对于部分反作弊对R3注入的强检测,R0层的技术已经无力应对了,必须得学会hypervisor了</strong></li>
<li><strong>本次学习主要参考<a href="https://space.bilibili.com/37877654/?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0">bilibili周壑老师的教程</a>,hyperplatform代码,书籍《处理器虚拟化技术》</strong></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="VT框架流程"><a href="#VT框架流程" class="headerlink" title="VT框架流程"></a>VT框架流程</h2><p><img src="/img/VT%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%20(%E4%B8%80)%20%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8EVMXON%20321f27818efb4d72835ff5b483a7725a/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<ul>
<li><del><strong>本人の粗略理解</strong>: 相比于直接用cpu模拟出的VMM,VT技术能使得Guest原生运行大部分指令,让虚拟机的性能得到巨大提升,并且能让虚拟机支持一些CPU的硬件特性</del></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="检测CPU是否能使用VT指令集"><a href="#检测CPU是否能使用VT指令集" class="headerlink" title="检测CPU是否能使用VT指令集"></a>检测CPU是否能使用VT指令集</h2><p>在此之前先需要了解一下SMX是个什么东西</p>
<h3 id="SMX"><a href="#SMX" class="headerlink" title="SMX"></a>SMX</h3><ul>
<li>SMX是面向**intel TXT(可信执行技术)**平台的编程接口,主要指令是<code>GETSEC</code></li>
<li>SMX指令集由<code>IA32_FEATURE_CONTROL MSR</code>决定是否开启,<strong>该MSR是不可写的</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>相关资料: </p>
<p><strong><code>intel手册 volume2 CHAPTER 6 SAFER MODE EXTENSIONS REFERENCE</code></strong></p>
<p><a href="https://www.intel.com/content/dam/www/public/us/en/documents/white-papers/trusted-execution-technology-security-paper.pdf"><code>**Intel® Trusted Execution Technology Hardware-based Technology for Enhancing Server Platform Security**</code></a></p>
<h3 id="IA32-FEATURE-CONTROL-结构"><a href="#IA32-FEATURE-CONTROL-结构" class="headerlink" title="IA32_FEATURE_CONTROL 结构"></a>IA32_FEATURE_CONTROL 结构</h3><p><img src="/img/VT%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%20(%E4%B8%80)%20%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8EVMXON%20321f27818efb4d72835ff5b483a7725a/Untitled%201.png" alt="Untitled"></p>
<h3 id="检测支持"><a href="#检测支持" class="headerlink" title="检测支持"></a>检测支持</h3><ol>
<li>执行cpuid(eax=1)指令,返回的ecx第5位为1说明cpu支持vt指令集</li>
<li>检测IA32_FEATURE_CONTROL MSR的第0位(lock bit),如果该位是1说明主板bios中开启了vt功能</li>
<li>检测IA32_FEATURE_CONTROL MSR的第1位,如果为1,则允许在SMX指令<code>GETSEC[SENTER]</code>和<code>GETSEC[SEXIT]</code>之间使用VMX相关指令,<strong>执行VMX指令时会受到TXT技术的保护</strong></li>
<li>检测IA32_FEATURE_CONTROL MSR的第2位,如果为1,则允许在SMX指令<code>GETSEC[SENTER]</code>和<code>GETSEC[SEXIT]</code>之外使用VMX相关指令</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="VMXON"><a href="#VMXON" class="headerlink" title="VMXON"></a>VMXON</h2><ul>
<li>vmxon需要一块4kb内存来记录维护虚拟机状态,称为VMXON region</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="VMXON初始化过程"><a href="#VMXON初始化过程" class="headerlink" title="VMXON初始化过程"></a>VMXON初始化过程</h3><ol>
<li>为VMXON region申请一块4KB的内存,首4字节的[30:0]写入VMCS revision identifier,[31]=0</li>
<li>使用<code>IA32_VMX_CR0_FIXED0 (index 486H)</code> 和 <code>IA32_VMX_CR0_FIXED1 (index 487H)</code> 调整CR0</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">_CR0 cr0 = &#123; <span class="built_in">AsmReadCr0</span>() &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">_CR0 cr0_fixed0 = &#123; <span class="built_in">AsmReadMsr64</span>(Msr::kIa32VmxCr0Fixed0) &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">_CR0 cr0_fixed1 = &#123; <span class="built_in">AsmReadMsr64</span>(Msr::kIa32VmxCr0Fixed1) &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">_CR0 cr0_original = cr0;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cr0.all &amp;= cr0_fixed1.all;</span><br><span class="line">cr0.all |= cr0_fixed0.all;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">AsmWriteCr0</span>(cr0.all);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="3">
<li>使用<code>IA32_VMX_CR4_FIXED0 (index 488H)</code> 和 <code>IA32_VMX_CR4_FIXED1 (index 489H)</code> 调整CR4</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">_CR4 cr4 = &#123; <span class="built_in">AsmReadCr4</span>() &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">_CR4 cr4_fixed0 = &#123; <span class="built_in">AsmReadMsr64</span>(Msr::kIa32VmxCr4Fixed0) &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">_CR4 cr4_fixed1 = &#123; <span class="built_in">AsmReadMsr64</span>(Msr::kIa32VmxCr4Fixed1) &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">_CR4 cr4_original = cr4;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cr4.all &amp;= cr4_fixed1.all;</span><br><span class="line">cr4.all |= cr4_fixed0.all;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">AsmWriteCr4</span>(cr4.all);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="4">
<li><p>执行<code>vmxon</code>指令,参数传入VMXON region的物理地址,如果指令执行之后<code>RFLAGS.CF = 0</code>,则VMXON初始化成功</p>
</li>
<li><p>vmxon执行之后cpu进入<strong>vmx操作模式</strong>,期间<code>CR4.VMXE</code>不可设为0,否则会触发#GP,可以用<code>vmxoff</code>指令退出<strong>vmx操作模式</strong>,如果没有执行到<code>vmlanuch</code>,不会对系统正常运行造成影响</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p>相关资料: <strong><code>intel手册 volume3 31.5 VMM SETUP &amp; TEAR DOWN</code></strong></p>
<p>如发现本人有误解,请各位师傅们指出教导一下</p>]]></content>
